1	# Fat Marker CSS Reference
2	
3	Copy these exact styles into every generated FM HTML. These values are extracted from the Figma FM library and must not be approximated — use these exact hex values, font sizes, paddings, and border-radii.
4	
5	**HARD RULE — No extra colors.** Every color in FM output MUST be a `--fm-*` variable or a `var(--fm-*)` reference. This includes:
6	- Badge backgrounds and text → use `--fm-base-200`/`--fm-base-700`, not purple/teal/amber
7	- Status tags → use `--fm-base-200`/`--fm-base-800`, not green/blue/yellow
8	- Highlights → use `--fm-base-300`, not yellow
9	- Type indicators → differentiate by text label or icon, not by color
10	
11	If you find yourself typing a hex value that isn't in the palette below, STOP — it's wrong. Use `--fm-base-*` grayscale to differentiate elements. FM is intentionally monochrome with only `--fm-brand` blue as an accent.
12	
13	## Token Palette
14	
15	```css
16	/* -- FM Token Palette (from Figma FM library) -- */
17	:root {
18	  --fm-base-900:   #1A202C;
19	  --fm-base-800:   #2D3648;   /* Primary button fill, nav text */
20	  --fm-base-700:   #4A5468;
21	  --fm-base-600:   #717D96;
22	  --fm-base-500:   #A0ABC0;
23	  --fm-base-400:   #CBD2E0;   /* Borders, disabled fills */
24	  --fm-base-300:   #E2E7F0;
25	  --fm-base-200:   #EDF0F7;   /* Active nav bg, hover, dividers */
26	  --fm-base-100:   #F5F5FA;
27	  --fm-base-white: #FFFFFF;
28	  --fm-brand:      #0550DC;
29	  --fm-brand-dark: #0029A9;
30	  --fm-brand-light:#EDF6FF;
31	  --fm-text-primary:  #101828;
32	  --fm-text-secondary:#2D3648;
33	  --fm-text-tertiary: #475467;
34	  --fm-text-error:    #D92D20;
35	  --fm-text-light:    #6D6D6D;
36	  --fm-text-success:  #047800;
37	  --fm-border:     #CBD2E0;
38	  --fm-bg-grey:    #F5F5FA;
39	  --fm-placeholder: #A0ABC0;
40	  --fm-shadow-default: 0px 2px 8px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.13);
41	  --fm-radius:     6px;
42	}
43	```
44	
45	## Component Styles
46	
47	### FM App Header (WHITE bg, all variants)
48	
49	```css
50	.fm-app-header {
51	  width: 100%; height: 70px;
52	  background: var(--fm-base-white);
53	  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--fm-base-400);
54	  display: flex; align-items: center;
55	  padding: 16px 28px; gap: 12px;
56	}
57	.fm-app-header__logo {
58	  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
59	  mix-blend-mode: luminosity; flex-shrink: 0;
60	}
61	.fm-app-header__logo-icon {
62	  width: 30px; height: 25px;
63	  background: var(--fm-base-400); border-radius: 2px;
64	}
65	.fm-app-header__brand-text {
66	  display: flex; flex-direction: column; line-height: 1.2;
67	}
68	.fm-app-header__brand-line1 {
69	  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 400;
70	  color: var(--fm-base-700); letter-spacing: 0.2px;
71	}
72	.fm-app-header__brand-line2 {
73	  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--fm-base-900);
74	}
75	.fm-app-header__spacer { flex: 1; }
76	.fm-app-header__icon-btn {
77	  width: 24px; height: 24px;
78	  background: var(--fm-base-300); border-radius: 4px;
79	}
80	.fm-app-header__avatar {
81	  width: 36px; height: 36px;
82	  background: var(--fm-base-400); border-radius: 50%;
83	}
84	```
85	
86	### FM Side Navigation Bar
87	
88	```css
89	.fm-sidebar {
90	  width: 260px; background: var(--fm-base-white);
91	  padding: 28px 16px 8px 16px;
92	  display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-shrink: 0;
93	}
94	.fm-sidebar__section {
95	  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; flex: 1;
96	}
97	.fm-sidebar__section--bottom {
98	  flex: 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--fm-base-200);
99	  padding-top: 16px; margin-top: auto;
100	}
101	.fm-sidebar__item {
102	  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
103	  padding: 12px 8px 12px 16px; border-radius: 8px;
104	  font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--fm-base-800);
105	  letter-spacing: -0.14px; line-height: 1.5;
106	}
107	.fm-sidebar__item--active {
108	  background: var(--fm-base-200); font-weight: 600;
109	}
110	.fm-sidebar__icon {
111	  width: 20px; height: 20px;
112	  border: 1.5px solid var(--fm-base-500); border-radius: 4px;
113	  flex-shrink: 0;
114	}
115	.fm-sidebar__chevron {
116	  width: 20px; height: 20px; margin-left: auto;
117	  color: var(--fm-base-500); display: flex;
118	  align-items: center; justify-content: center;
119	  font-size: 14px; flex-shrink: 0;
120	}
121	```
122	
123	### FM Button
124	
125	```css
126	.fm-button {
127	  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
128	  gap: 10px; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 6px;
129	  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
130	  font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; letter-spacing: -0.32px;
131	  cursor: pointer; border: none; white-space: nowrap; height: 48px;
132	}
133	.fm-button--primary { background: var(--fm-base-800); color: white; }
134	.fm-button--secondary { background: white; color: var(--fm-base-800); }
135	.fm-button--outline {
136	  background: transparent; color: var(--fm-base-800);
137	  border: 2px solid var(--fm-base-800);
138	}
139	.fm-button--text {
140	  background: transparent; color: var(--fm-brand);
141	  padding: 10px 4px; border: none; height: auto;
142	}
143	.fm-button--disabled { background: var(--fm-base-400); color: white; cursor: not-allowed; }
144	.fm-button--sm {
145	  padding: 8px 16px; font-size: 14px;
146	  letter-spacing: -0.28px; height: auto;
147	}
148	```
149	
150	### FM Page Header
151	
152	```css
153	.fm-page-header__title {
154	  font-weight: 600; font-size: 24px; line-height: 34.32px;
155	  color: var(--fm-text-primary);
156	}
157	.fm-page-header__subtitle {
158	  font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.88px;
159	  color: var(--fm-text-tertiary); margin-top: 4px;
160	}
161	```
162	
163	### FM Input Label
164	
165	```css
166	.fm-input-label { display: flex; gap: 4px; align-items: baseline; }
167	.fm-input-label__text {
168	  font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px;
169	  color: #1A202C;
170	}
171	.fm-input-label__required {
172	  font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; color: #D92D20;
173	}
174	```
175	
176	### FM Text Input
177	
178	```css
179	.fm-text-input {
180	  width: 100%; height: 40px;
181	  border: 1px solid var(--fm-border); border-radius: 6px;
182	  padding: 8px 12px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
183	  font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.28px; line-height: 22px;
184	  color: #1A202C; background: white;
185	}
186	.fm-text-input::placeholder { color: var(--fm-placeholder); }
187	```
188	
189	### FM Alert
190	
191	```css
192	.fm-alert {
193	  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
194	  padding: 12px 16px; height: 48px; border-radius: 6px;
195	  box-shadow: 0px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
196	}
197	.fm-alert--success { background: #EDF0F7; }
198	.fm-alert--error { background: #FCF3F3; }
199	.fm-alert--info { background: #EDF0F7; }
200	.fm-alert__text { font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; color: #1A202C; }
201	```
202	
203	### FM Tag
204	
205	```css
206	.fm-tag {
207	  display: inline-flex; align-items: center;
208	  padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 9999px;
209	  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 20px;
210	}
211	```
212	
213	### Generation Card
214	
215	```css
216	.gen-card {
217	  width: 280px; flex-shrink: 0; background: var(--fm-base-800); border-radius: 12px;
218	  padding: 20px 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;
219	  align-self: flex-start;
220	}
221	.gen-card__label {
